mapper.select: SELECT 'S' AUD, IDX,ID,PW,NAME,AUTH,TEL_NO,REMARK,USE_YN FROM mb_subject WHERE NAME LIKE CONCAT('%', #{value},'%') ORDER BY NAME, ID

SELECT 'S' AUD , CONCAT(A.PROGCD01,') ', X.progname) AS MENU01 , CONCAT(A.PROGCD02,') ', Y.progname) AS MENU02 , CONCAT(A.PROGCD03,') ', A.PROGNAME) PROGNAME , A.PROGID , CASE WHEN B.PROGID IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END CHK , CASE WHEN B.PROGID IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END CHK_O FROM mb_proglist A JOIN mb_proglist X ON X.progcd03 = '' AND X.progcd02 = '' AND X.progcd01 = A.PROGCD01 LEFT JOIN mb_proglist Y ON Y.progcd03 = '' AND Y.progcd02 = A.progcd02 AND Y.progcd01 = A.PROGCD01 LEFT JOIN mb_pempower B ON A.PROGID = B.PROGID AND B.PUSERID = #{value} WHERE A.PROGID != '' AND A.USEYN = 'Y' ORDER BY MENU01, MENU02, PROGNAME
SELECT a.userid_fr as USERID, s.name as USERNAME FROM mb_nrcdpower a JOIN mb_subject s on a.userid_fr = s.id WHERE a.progid = 'CSBR1050' AND a.userid = #{value} ORDER BY USERNAME
SELECT id as USERID, s.name as USERNAME FROM mb_subject s WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM mb_nrcdpower x WHERE x.progid ='CSBR1050' AND x.userid = #{value} AND x.userid_fr = s.id) ORDER BY USERNAME
select count(*) from mb_subject where id=#{value}
select idx , id , pw , name , auth , tel_no , remark , use_yn from mb_subject where id= #{value}
mapper.delete: delete from mb_pempower where puserid=#{puserid} and UPPER(progid)=#{progid} and 1=1
mapper.select: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(INSERT_DATE,'%Y-%m-%d') AS USEDATE , case dayofweek(INSERT_DATE) when 1 then '일' when 2 then '월' when 3 then '화' when 4 then '수' when 5 then '목' when 6 then '금' else '토' end AS WEEK ,COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM mb_usedlog A JOIN mb_subject B ON B.ID=A.USERID JOIN mb_proglist C ON C.PROGID=A.USEPGID WHERE USEDBUTTON = 'EXCEL' AND INSERT_DATE BETWEEN '${sd} 00:00:00' AND '${ed} 23:59:59' ${snameQuery} ${spnameQuery} GROUP BY USEDATE ORDER BY USEDATE DESC

SELECT 'S' AUD, A.USERID,NAME,PROGNAME ,DATE_FORMAT(A.INSERT_DATE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS INSERT_DATE FROM mb_usedlog A JOIN mb_subject B ON B.ID=A.USERID JOIN mb_proglist C ON C.PROGID=A.USEPGID WHERE USEDBUTTON = 'EXCEL' AND INSERT_DATE LIKE CONCAT(#{d} ,'%') ${snameQuery} ${spnameQuery} ORDER BY INSERT_DATE
mapper.update: update mb_etccd set CDNM=#{nm} where KDCD='0000' and CDBS = #{bs} and 1=1
mapper.insert: insert into mb_etccd (KDCD, CDBS, CDNM, SORTNO, UNUSEYN, DESC1, DESC2, DESC3, MODIFYUSID, MODIFYDATE) values ('0000',#{bs},#{nm},0,'N','','','',#{modifyusid},now())
insert into mb_etccd (KDCD, CDBS, CDNM, SORTNO, UNUSEYN, DESC1, DESC2, DESC3, MODIFYUSID, MODIFYDATE) values (#{selcode}, #{bs}, #{nm}, #{sno}, #{uyn}, #{d1}, #{d2}, #{d3}, #{modifyusid}, now())
mapper.select: SELECT DISTINCT a.USEUSERID USERID , s.name USERNM , CASE WHEN a.STDTE IS NOT NULL AND a.CSDTE IS NULL THEN '접속' ELSE '종료' END USERUSYN FROM mb_useprogram a JOIN mb_subject s on s.ID = a.USEUSERID WHERE a.USEYMD = #{sd} ${stypeQuery}

SELECT CASE WHEN a.USEPGID = '00000000' AND a.CSDTE IS NULL THEN '접속:시작' WHEN a.USEPGID = '00000000' AND a.CSDTE IS NOT NULL THEN '접속:시작-종료' ELSE p.progname END PGNM , a.IPADDR , a.MACADDR , DATE_FORMAT(a.STDTE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') STDTE , DATE_FORMAT(a.CSDTE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') CSDTE FROM mb_useprogram a LEFT JOIN mb_proglist p on p.progid = a.USEPGID WHERE a.USEYMD = #{sdate} AND a.USEUSERID = #{id} ORDER BY STDTE, CSDTE
SELECT 'S' AUD, IDX, PROGCD01,PROGCD02,PROGCD03,PROGID,PROGNAME, USEYN FROM mb_proglist ORDER BY PROGCD01,PROGCD02,PROGCD03,PROGID
SELECT id as USERID, s.name as USERNAME FROM mb_pempower a JOIN mb_subject s on a.puserid = s.id WHERE progid = #{value} ORDER BY USERNAME
SELECT id as USERID, s.name as USERNAME FROM mb_subject s WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM mb_pempower x WHERE x.progid = #{value} AND x.puserid = s.id) ORDER BY USERNAME
mapper.insert: insert into mb_proglist (progcd01, progcd02, progcd03, progid, progname, useyn) values (#{cd1}, #{cd2}, #{cd3}, #{pid}, #{pname}, #{puseyn})
